entry.title: Hello World
entry.content:
Hello World!

I didn’t write any blog posts over a year. During these time, I used to think I must write some notes as blog posts for future reference. But it didn’t happen in reality.

If you didn’t start anything, it won’t happen anything. We used to forget tiny things easily. We know it is useful in some way but we used to forget. This is my blog, a bag which contains this tiny things.
